http://www.floridatradesites.com/* https://www.floridatradesites.com/:splat 301!

# Short demo links for SMS: /d/<id> serves d.html, which looks <id> up in
# demos.json and hands off to demo.html with that lead's query string.
# Status 200 (rewrite, not redirect) so the short path stays in the address bar.
# ONE wildcard rule on purpose -- per-lead rules would be 1253 entries and
# Netlify degrades past roughly 1000.
/d/*  /d.html  200
